OL,3,CRoy Hodgson, 78, announced as Bristol
OL,4,CCity Head Coach as Gerhard Struber
OL,5,Csacked
OL,7,FBristol City Football Club has sacked
OL,8,Fhead coach Gerhard Struber and
OL,9,Finstalled former England boss Roy
OL,10,FHodgson as interim head coach.
OL,12,FIt sees the 78-year-old return to the
OL,13,Fclub which gave him his first England
OL,14,Fmanagement role in 1982.
OL,16,FAssistant Head Coach Bernd Eibler will
OL,17,Falso leave with immediate effect,
OL,18,Fafter the club said recent
OL,19,Fperformances by the Robins "have not
OL,20,Fmet expectations".
