OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774861565
OL,3,CRoy Hodgson, 78, announced as Bristol
OL,4,CCity Head Coach as Gerhard Struber
OL,5,Csacked
OL,7,F"I would like to thank Gerhard and
OL,8,FBernd for their hard work over the
OL,9,Fpast nine months and we wish them all
OL,10,Fthe best," said Charlie Boss, City CEO.
OL,12,F"Roy's appointment is about more than
OL,13,Fthe results of the next seven games.
OL,15,F"Over the remainder of the season, he
OL,16,Fwill help us set the standards and
OL,17,Fvalues at the club that we will need
OL,18,Fto be successful going forwards."
