OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774861565
OL,3,CRoy Hodgson, 78, announced as Bristol
OL,4,CCity Head Coach as Gerhard Struber
OL,5,Csacked
OL,7,FHodgson will lead the men's first team
OL,8,Fthrough their next seven games until
OL,9,Fthe end of the season.
OL,11,FHe most recently managed Crystal
OL,12,FPalace, before stepping down in 2024
OL,13,Fafter he fell ill and was taken to
OL,14,Fhospital during a training session.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
